summary: Just a simple Wood Elf follower.
descriptionHtml:
Just a simple follower, using the vanilla framework. Her skills are archery, light armor, and sneak. She is located in Jorrvaskr (next one will be somewhere else I promise), and is technically a Companion, but should follow you immediately.

In the screenshots I'm using [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/30181/?]Alt Navetsea UNP Seamless by Alt3rn1ty[/url] with [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/31954/?]BI Phenotypes by betterbecause[/url] (base version) installed over it. They work well together.
I'm also using [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/49069/?]Improved Eyes Skyrim by missjennabee[/url] which made her eyes green, but they were golden brown on my husband's computer, so that's most likely the color someone not using that mod will see.

Let me know if there are any issues.
author: Indiwolf14
